  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q100.a003.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">a soldier at any time at his own charges? Who feedeth the flock, and eateth not of the milk of the flock?" Hence it is simoniacal to sell or buy that which is spiritual in such like actions; but to receive or give something for the support of those who minister spiritual things in accorda</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
</edge>
