  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">rving who throws the highest score; or by observing what catches the eye when one opens a book, all of which are named "sortilege." Accordingly it is clear that there are three kinds of divination . The first is when the demons are invoked openly, this comes under the head of "necromancy"</data>
