  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that religion does not direct man to God alone. It is written ( James 1:27 ): "Religion clean and undefiled before God and the Father is this, to visit the fatherless and widows in their tribulation, and to</data>
