  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q081.a007.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that religion has not an external act. It is written ( John 4:24 ): " God is a spirit, and they that adore Him, must adore Him in spirit and in truth ." Now external acts pertain, not to the spirit but to t</data>
