  <data key="d14"></data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q081.a008.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that religion is not the same as sanctity. Religion is a special virtue , as stated above ( Article 4 ): whereas sanctity is a general virtue , because it makes us faithful, and fulfil our just obligations </data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
