  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q081.a005.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( Article 4 ) religion pays due worship to God . Hence two things are to be considered in religion: first that which it offers to God , viz. worship, and this is by way of matter and</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
