  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q083.a016.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that sinners impetrate nothing from God by their prayers . It is written ( John 9:31 ): "We know that God doth not hear sinners"; and this agrees with the saying of Proverbs 28:9 , "He that turneth away his</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
