  <data key="d14"></data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q083.a017.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that the parts of prayer are unfittingly described as supplications, prayers , intercessions, and thanksgivings. Supplication would seem to be a kind of adjuration. Yet, according to Origen (Super Matth. Tr</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
