  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q083.a001.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">According to Cassiodorus [Comment. in Psalm 38:13 " prayer [oratio] is spoken reason [oris ratio]." Now the speculative and practical reason differ in this, that the speculative merely apprehends its object, whereas th</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
