  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">The Lord's Prayer is most perfect, because, as Augustine says (ad Probam Ep. cxxx, 12), "if we pray rightly and fittingly, we can say nothing else but what is contained in this</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
