  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q083.a010.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( Article 1 ) prayer is an act of reason , and consists in beseeching a superior; just as command is an act of reason , whereby an inferior is directed to something. Accordingly pr</data>
