  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">This question applies chiefly to vocal prayer . Accordingly we must observe that a thing is necessary in two ways. First, a thing is necessary because thereby the end is better obtained: and thus attention</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
