  <data key="d14"></data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q086.a001.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that men are not bound by precept to make oblations. Men are not bound, at the time of the Gospel, to observe the ceremonial precepts of the Old Law , as stated above ( I-II:103:3 ; I-II:103:4 ). Now the of</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
<edge source="st.ii-ii.q086" target="st.ii-ii.q086.a002" id="structural.st.ii-ii.q086.contains.st.ii-ii.q086.a002">
