  <data key="d14"></data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q086.a002.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that oblations are not due to priests alone. For chief among oblations would seem to be those that are deputed to the sacrifices of victims. Now whatever is given to the poor is called a "victim in Scriptur</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
