  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">We use words, in speaking to God , for one reason, and in speaking to man , for another reason. For when speaking to man we use words in order to tell him our thoughts which are unknown to him. Wherefore we praise a man with our lips, in order that he or other</data>
