  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( Article 1 ), the praise of the voice is necessary in order to arouse man's devotion towards God . Wherefore whatever is useful in conducing to this result is becomingly adopted in the divine praises. Now it is evident that the human soul is m</data>
