  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q092.a001.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that superstition is not a vice contrary to religion. One contrary is not included in the definition of the other. But religion is included in the definition of superstition : for the latter is defined as b</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
