  <data key="d11">st.ii-ii.q099.a003</data>
  <data key="d12">II-II q.99 a.3 — The species of sacrilege</data>
  <data key="d13">article</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q099.a003.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that the species of sacrilege are not distinguished according to the sacred things. Material diversity does not differentiate species , if the formal aspect remains the same. Now there would seem to be the </data>
