  <data key="d14"></data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q099.a004.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that the punishment of sacrilege should not be pecuniary. A pecuniary punishment is not wont to be inflicted for a criminal fault. But sacrilege is a criminal fault, wherefore it is punished by capital sent</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
