  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( Article 1 ), the sin of sacrilege consists in the irreverent treatment of a sacred thing. Now reverence is due to a sacred thing by reason of its holiness : and consequently the species of sacr</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
